Challenge Description

CyberHunt2 is a network-based challenge focusing on exposed services and weak credentials. The objective is to enumerate open services, identify misconfigurations, reuse discovered credentials, and escalate privileges to obtain both user and root flags.

The hint suggests that weak credentials left during testing may lead to system compromise.

